			<div class="content" id="post-content-3824822">
									

<p>Well I did like the idea and the execution but, as a 001 (I mean it's better than some other proposals <em>not naming names</em>) I just don't like it, I don't really get why this should be an scp, specially a 001 proposal. It would probably work better as a normal skip or a tale. <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">So no voting for now</span> fuck it I'll upvote it.</p>
<p>Also I don't know if I like this trend of turning GOIs into 001s, it worked with the Scarlett King because it is tied to the existence of the foundation.</p>

							</div>

								
